headline: Trimble Announces 2024 Construction Innovation Award Winners
summary: Trimble® (Nasdaq: TRMB) today announced winners of the annual Trimble Construction Innovation Awards, recognizing exceptional use of Trimble technology on workflows, processes and projects by North American customers.
